\c 114
\s Simba raJehovha parwendo rwaVaIsraeri
\p
\v 1 Pakubuda kwaIsraeri paEgipita, imba yaJakove pavanhu verurimi rwevechirudzi.
\v 2 Judha wakava imba yake tsvene, Israeri akava ushe hwake.
\p
\v 3 Gungwa rakaona ndokutiza; Joridhani rwakadzokera shure.
\v 4 Makomo akapembera semakondohwe, nezvikomo semakwayana.
\p
\v 5 Chii kwauri, gungwa, kuti utize? Newe Joridhani, \add kuti\add* udzokere shure?
\v 6 Nemwi makomo, zvamunopembera samakondohwe; nemwi zvikomo, samakwayana?
\p
\v 7 Bvunda iwe pasi, pamberi paShe, pamberi paMwari waJakove.
\v 8 Iye akashandura dombo, rikava dziva remvura, (add missing).
